    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes a packet explosion problem that can occur with mutual encapsulation of protocols (A encapsulates B and B encapsulates A).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
